review_blob: Aroma is very nice citrus and spice. Head is medium with small white bubbles. Mouthfeel is very nice from the carbonation and citrus bitterness. Overall a very tasty Belgian triple.
beer_name: Unibroue Cest Pas La Fin du Monde!

review_blob: Excellent dunkel! The aroma is dominated by caramel, some roasty and chocolate. Very little to no hops in aroma or in taste. Pours a clear clean brown with a medium head. taste is dominated by the malty caramel and chocolate. Overall a very good dunkel.
Good color with a nice white head. Moderate hoppy aroma dominated by the citrus hops. Heavy citrus flavors contradicts the hops. Ok to drink but an odd combination.
